ZH: 我要举报这起偷窃案。
EN: I want to report this theft case.

ZH: 请你举报有人在保护区捕猎。
EN: Please report someone hunting in the protected area.

ZH: 他们应该举报这种违法行为。
EN: They should report this illegal activity.

ZH: 他被邻居举报偷窃。
EN: He was reported by the neighbors for theft.

ZH: 我们鼓励大家积极举报腐败现象。
EN: We encourage everyone to actively report cases of corruption.

ZH: 她勇敢地举报了公司内部的欺诈行为。
EN: She bravely reported the fraud within the company.

ZH: 请大家共同举报违法行为，保护社会安宁。
EN: Please report illegal activities together to protect social order.

ZH: 如果你发现了垃圾倾倒现象，请及时举报。
EN: If you see illegal dumping, please report it promptly.

ZH: 希望政府能够建立更加便捷的举报渠道。
EN: I hope the government can establish a more convenient reporting channel.

ZH: 他是一名勇敢的告密者，屡次举报犯罪行为。
EN: He is a brave whistleblower, repeatedly reporting criminal activities.

ZH: 他因为举报贪污腐败被陷害。
EN: He was framed for reporting corruption.

ZH: 我们的公司有一个匿名举报制度。
EN: Our company has an anonymous reporting system.

ZH: 请您举报任何线索，帮助解救被困人员。
EN: Please report any clues to help rescue the trapped individuals.

ZH: 他表示愿意出庭作证举报涉嫌人贩活动。
EN: He expressed willingness to testify in court to report suspected human trafficking activities.

ZH: 大家一定要勇敢站出来举报不法行为。
EN: Everyone must bravely come forward to report illegal activities.

ZH: 她因举报贪腐受到了很多威胁。
EN: She received many threats after reporting corruption.

ZH: 为了社会的和谐发展，我们每个人都有责任举报不法行为。
EN: For the harmonious development of society, we all have a responsibility to report illegal activities.

ZH: 希望更多人加入举报行动，揭露不法分子。
EN: I hope more people will join in the reporting action and expose the criminals.

ZH: 这起可疑行为需要有人举报。
EN: This suspicious behavior needs to be reported by someone.
